name: Warung Makan Muslim Lalanglinggah
address: GX62+7H7, Jl. Raya Denpasar - Gilimanuk, Lalanglinggah, Kec. Selemadeg Bar., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 80162, Indonesia
review 1: Convenient warung along the busy Gilimanuk road. It's open 24/7, but of course the menu is somewhat limited. The ayam goreng with the sayur (vegetables) I had was good. The place features many bonsai trees, which is interesting. Bike-friendly.
review 2: Fantastic ikan bakar nyat nyat, never had such good one with so tasty sauce and garnishing
review 3: I highly recommend this place when you are on a long drive, in my case from Kuta to Gilimanuk, and want to have a rest and something to eat or drink (or both). The Bami goreng I had was one of the best I had in a long time. Also the staff is super friendly and helpful. They made a form of Thai tea for me even though it wasn't on the menu. Very kind and lovely place. ❤️
review 4: On the mainstreet, they have good food but small portion
